At X-Steem-Crew, our mission is to make life easy and simple so that people can concentrate on what really matters in their life.
We fulfill this mission through our PC application, X-steem-Notes.
X-steem-Notes not only makes people effortlessly stay organized but also make sure that they never miss important things. X-steem-Notes aim to make X-steem-Note one of the most populous notepad apps on PC.
Mobile application to follow, and it would be made valuable to steemians, where Steemians would be able to save posts and save drafts for future use in an organized way.
X-steem-Crew was founded in 2014.
